THE GAME
--------

  'Try_Angle' is played on a triangular-shaped board; the idea is
to move from the top triangle to an 'exit' triangle located on the
lowest row of the game board. As you leave a triangle, if it has
no number on it, it will disappear. If there's a number displayed
on it, leaving it will make that number decrease by 1 unit. That
number indicates how many times you can go on that triangle, until
it disappears.

  Some triangles have coloured numbers, so you must go on these
triangles the indicated number of times before they disappear. If
you get to the exit triangle without clearing all the triangles
with coloured numbers, the game would be over.

  When playing, be careful not to trap yourself on an isolated
triangle.

  Have fun!

